{"tid":1667384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有CC台有班人渣 為咗奶美國就要學LBJ咁 叫人唔好撐美國","createTime":"2019-10-21T12:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:22:38.000Z","uid":220701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cec939c14ca68532d7954f3585cf819bf2f44666","tid":1667384,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"我冇咩嘢想同佢哋講呀<br />\n不過做人做到咁無恥 你就賤撚到同POPO一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fed1e50384d715d5b6dc0865709ffd28dac6454","tid":1667384,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"打錯<br />\n係叫人唔好撐加泰"},{"pid":"9372dd69a9b0ef32f9be93ad742a6de547436425","tid":1667384,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"5e72a571449eccc6502ead20404466a2c4e2b918","tid":1667384,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"7057dae4f6e9df562591559d60d92d1434b1ad50","tid":1667384,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be7bb494693ea452df3add8f3354cca852abb729","tid":1667384,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"[核彈]一文道破為何時事台瘋狂攻擊切割加泰人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667326</a><br />\n<br />\n支共01"},{"pid":"7dc3e09b2c1e23e192bec4723c52428948d3240c","tid":1667384,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"就算撐又點 如果美國有心撐香港會避重就輕扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"0b5d0b906aaffb725fea6a057f87caafa2d2bfcd","tid":1667384,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}